#ad Radio Flyer’s Ultimate Go-Kart is a HUGE hit in our neighborhood! We hosted a really fun test drive party. All the kiddos gave it two thumbs up and five stars ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️!! Even the teenagers came around to check it out. 
Give your kiddos the gift of hours of exciting outdoor play and #unwrapradioflyer this Holiday season. 🎁 🏎 
The awesome electric car from @radioflyerinc can be plugged in to recharge and runs for hours! The #radioflyer Ultimate Go-Kart  has so many wonderful safety features, including a sturdy steel frame. Kiddos will stay safe with the parent-controlled speed lock, seat belt, and cool high-visibility racing flag. There are large rear wheels and great rubber traction.  It’s perfect for kiddos ages 3-8 and holds up to 81 pounds. The car can be set at 2.5 , 5, and 8 mph. It has single speed reverse.  Both boys are having a blast racing each other and driving around.  This is #kidapproved and a definite #momwin. Check it out for the kiddos on your list and give them the ULTIMATE Holiday gift.🎁 You can find it at https://www.radioflyer.com and 
https://www.walmart.com 🏎

https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket (Ad) Get your kiddos outside and active with the @theoriginalstomprocket from @target. This makes a fantastic holiday gift for ages 5 and up. We received the Stomp Rocket Stunt Planes High Flying Planes with Launch Pad 3pk.  https://www.target.com/s?searchTerm=stomp+rocket 🚀
Dominic and Scotty are having a blast stomping, jumping, and running to launch the rockets.  Active play is so important for kids. Having them participate in #unpluggedplay is beneficial for their overall development. This toy combines working on #stemlearning and #grossmotorskills all while having a great time! 🚀
I love that the Stomp Rocket 🚀 has kiddos using their brain and muscle power. The boys are having a lot of fun trying to launch the rocket at different angles, into a box, and the basketball hoop. It’s great watching the boys thinking, discussing, and trying new ideas with this toy. As a mom and early childhood educator this is the type of toy I get excited about! 🚀
